data.description: Amazing home on cul-de-sac minutes from Spring Creek Park! Gorgeous move in ready 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom beauty. The main floor offers an open floor concept full of natural light. The great room features a built-in entertainment center and 3-sided gas fireplace that opens to the dining area. Nice open eat-in kitchen with granite tile countertops, new 2022 stainless steel appliances with gas stove, and an abundance of cabinet storage. 1/2 bath and laundry on the main level with large coat/utility closet. Upstairs you'll find three large bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a open, loft-style bonus room perfect for a home office, play room or craft space. Amazing custom deck and patio! Recent upgrades & updates include; newer flooring throughout; carpet and laminate, newer whole house attic fan, newer light fixtures in Kitchen, over dining, entry way and upstairs hallway, newer interior paint (all ceilings, baseboards and walls) front door and garage door painted. Keyless entry, Google Nest video camera video door bell, Google Nest smoke detectors, newer washer and dryer included. Don't wait on this one.
